{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"边缘服务业务接口文档","description":"保留监控页面与本地运维会直接使用的接口。文档中的 `server_task_id` 均表示服务端下发的任务 ID，不是 lesson_id，也不是本地数据库自增 id。其中查询参数 `id` 的格式固定为 `{server_task_id}-{STEP}`，例如 `4-DOWNLOAD`、`4-TRANSCODE`。","version":"1.0.0"},"paths":{"/api/task/video":{"get":{"tags":["业务接口"],"summary":"获取视频文件","description":"按业务类型获取视频内容。当 `source=source` 时返回源视频 MP4；当 `source=hls` 时返回转码后 HLS 的 master 播放列表。","operationId":"api_task_video_api_task_video_get","parameters":[{"name":"id","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"服务端任务标识，不是 lesson_id。格式固定为 `{server_task_id}-{STEP}`。示例：`4-DOWNLOAD` 表示任务 4 的源视频；`4-TRANSCODE` 表示任务 4 的转码视频。","examples":{"source_video":{"summary":"源视频","value":"4-DOWNLOAD"},"hls_video":{"summary":"转码后 HLS 视频","value":"4-TRANSCODE"}},"default":"","title":"Id"},"description":"服务端任务标识，不是 lesson_id。格式固定为 `{server_task_id}-{STEP}`。示例：`4-DOWNLOAD` 表示任务 4 的源视频；`4-TRANSCODE` 表示任务 4 的转码视频。"},{"name":"source","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"视频来源类型。`source` 表示源视频 MP4，`hls` 表示转码后的 HLS master 播放列表。","examples":{"source":{"summary":"源视频","value":"source"},"hls":{"summary":"转码后 HLS","value":"hls"}},"default":"source","title":"Source"},"description":"视频来源类型。`source` 表示源视频 MP4，`hls` 表示转码后的 HLS master 播放列表。"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"返回视频文件或 HLS master 播放列表","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"400":{"description":"参数格式错误，例如 id 不是 `{server_task_id}-{STEP}` 格式"},"404":{"description":"对应视频文件不存在"},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/task/subtitle-vtt":{"get":{"tags":["业务接口"],"summary":"获取字幕文件（VTT）","description":"按业务类型获取字幕 VTT 文件。当 `source=source` 时返回源视频对应字幕；当 `source=hls` 时返回 HLS 目录中的字幕。","operationId":"api_task_subtitle_vtt_api_task_subtitle_vtt_get","parameters":[{"name":"id","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"服务端任务标识，不是 lesson_id。格式固定为 `{server_task_id}-{STEP}`。示例：`4-DOWNLOAD` 表示任务 4 的源视频字幕；`4-TRANSCODE` 表示任务 4 的 HLS 字幕。","examples":{"source_subtitle":{"summary":"源视频字幕","value":"4-DOWNLOAD"},"hls_subtitle":{"summary":"HLS 字幕","value":"4-TRANSCODE"}},"default":"","title":"Id"},"description":"服务端任务标识，不是 lesson_id。格式固定为 `{server_task_id}-{STEP}`。示例：`4-DOWNLOAD` 表示任务 4 的源视频字幕；`4-TRANSCODE` 表示任务 4 的 HLS 字幕。"},{"name":"source","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"字幕来源类型。`source` 表示源视频字幕，`hls` 表示 HLS 字幕。","examples":{"source":{"summary":"源视频字幕","value":"source"},"hls":{"summary":"HLS 字幕","value":"hls"}},"default":"hls","title":"Source"},"description":"字幕来源类型。`source` 表示源视频字幕，`hls` 表示 HLS 字幕。"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"返回 VTT 字幕文件","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"400":{"description":"参数格式错误"},"404":{"description":"字幕文件不存在"},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/server-artifacts/{server_task_id}":{"get":{"tags":["业务接口"],"summary":"获取任务产物汇总信息","description":"返回某个服务端任务对应的业务产物访问地址汇总，包括源视频、HLS 视频、源字幕、HLS 字幕、语音转写报告、视频分析报告等。","operationId":"api_server_artifacts_api_server_artifacts__server_task_id__get","parameters":[{"name":"server_task_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","description":"服务端任务 ID，不是 lesson_id，也不是本地 edge_stream_task 表的自增主键。示例：`4`。","examples":{"task_id":{"summary":"任务 4","value":4}},"title":"Server Task Id"},"description":"服务端任务 ID，不是 lesson_id，也不是本地 edge_stream_task 表的自增主键。示例：`4`。"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"返回产物地址汇总 JSON","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"404":{"description":"未找到对应任务"},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/analysis-report/{server_task_id}":{"get":{"tags":["业务接口"],"summary":"获取视频分析报告","description":"返回指定服务端任务对应课次的视频分析 HTML 报告。报告按课次共享，不是按单个本地 task_id 存储。","operat